abstracts.abstract: BOARD BILL #  58              INTRODUCED BY: ALDERMAN FRANK WILLIAMSON    An ordinance authorizing and directing the Mayor and Comptroller of the City of St. Louis to execute, upon receipt of and in consideration of the sum of   Two Thousand Seven Hundred Dollars ($2,700) and other good and valuable consideration, a Quit Claim Deed to remise, release and forever quit-claim unto SUNLITE PROPERTIES, LLC , whose address is 15280 Clayton Road Ballwin Mo. 63011 certain City-owned property located in City Block 3792, which property is known by address of  5279 Page Blvd .
